content:
Here is the simple list of components of the eye exam from the IHE GEE project which could organize ophthalmology observation resources:
Refractive Measurements
Lensometry Measurements
Intraocular pressure
Visual Field
Eye External
Lacrimal
Pupils
Ocular alignment and motility
Anterior segment
Posterior segment
Ancillary Testing
